msgid "Write Python code to fetch and transform data. Available globals:<br>• client: API client for the selected data source<br>• table: Write data to warehouse. Methods: insert(data, overwrite=False)<br>• state: Persist data between runs. Methods: get(key, default=None), set(key, value), delete(key), clear()<br>• secrets: Access secret keys. Methods: get(key)<br>• log(message): Log execution messages"
